    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "Properties",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Known Names",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kabukimono",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Kabukimono\" referred mostly to those who wore vibrant colors and behaved in a peculiar manner. The puppet was called Kabukimono by the Tatarasuna workers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kunikuzushi",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "In Inazuma's traditional theater, there is a certain character known as \"Kunikuzushi.\" Such characters are often schemers and usurpers of nations. Kabukimono chose this name at the end of his wandering.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Scaramouche",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Balladeer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The puppet's name when he joined the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7106,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/23/237301566/38c409297992d7a782f0f1312f311707_3548311870444408788.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Fatui",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and became the sixth of the Fatui Harbingers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Wanderer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Scaramouche became the Wanderer after he erased himself from",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7087,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/24/237301566/aa06aa829f5a3a926aef88750adb81f2_3960309425065670916.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Irminsul",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7470,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Beelzebul",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Raiden Ei created Scaramouche as a prototype puppet to prove the concept of creating a puppet body.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Katsuragi",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Niwa",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mikoshi Nagamasa",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Miyazaki",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The people from Tatarasuna who found the puppet and became his family.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yae Miko_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Yae Miko",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When Kabukimono asked for help for Tatarasuna, Yae Miko sent people to their aid immediately, but he was convinced that the Shogunate had forsaken Tatarasuna. When he left Tatarasuna after Niwa's death, she didn't want to further disturb him and merely sent someone to return the feather to him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When The Balladeer threatened the Traveler's life, Yae Miko exchanged the life for the Electro",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4935,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/94376896/d233949972be14fcf0feb738a9b67efa_4817492893140404510.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Gnosis",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7106,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/23/237301566/38c409297992d7a782f0f1312f311707_3548311870444408788.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Fatui",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A few years after three betrayals and leaving Tatarasuna, the puppet joined the Fatui and became the sixth Fatui Harbinger.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7475,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "The Doctor",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Fatui Harbinger who tested on Scaramouche to find a technology to create the \"segments\" of himself. He unlocked the seal on Scaramouche's body, causing his abilities to increase greatly, and later tried to turn the Balladeer into a new Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2975,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/03/35428890/86791657203a69e453d8e217414b3f9e_6244827810099144009.png",
                      "menu_id": 7,
                      "name": "Shouki no Kami, the Prodigal",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A mechanical body for a new Archon created by the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7034,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/04/237301566/2285a2d002f2043abe9bddf65a46f891_6956832860262339103.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Sumeru Akademiya",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7471,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Buer",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The God of Wisdom defeated Scaramouche and took the Electro Gnosis away.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2968,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/05/35428890/24d97a22be742fb732ea96f625d1faac_2495743636540582085.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Wanderer",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Scaramouche's new personality after he erased himself from Irminsul. He's currently studying at the Sumeru Akademiya, Vahumana Darshan.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 37,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Mona_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Mona",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Fischl",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Scaramouche met with the Traveler, Mona, and Fischl on his expedition to study the fallen stars. With her abilities, Mona realized the danger of the Harbinger and teleported them away.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
